  "text": "We will make some preparations in Sections 7.1, 7.2 and 7.3 , and give the proof of Theorem 7.1 in Section 7.4. In Section 7.5 we will apply Theorem 7.1 to show that discrete triangulated categories in the sense of [CITATION_1] are t-discrete, provided that it is part of an ST-pair.",
